phrases: Sarah and Lola competed in a receptionist battle.
I wanted my receptionist, Lola, to win, so I went looking for rare items,
and on the seventh floor of the hidden dungeon I visited...
I guess someone decided to recreate a forest on this floor?
I am only at level 63 right now.
I need to turn back for now.
Wh-What is childhood Emma doing here?
Here is my birthday gift to you.
I picked it because it is the same color as your eyes.
I promise I will get you something nice for your birthday, too!
A trap in the hidden dungeon?
Having witnessed how powerful you are, I have a request.
Th-This seems kind of out of nowhere...
If nothing is done, I am going to die.
S-So what are you trying to do there?
Showing you that I completely surrender.
I-I will at least hear you out.
You see, I am actually a great tree within this forest.
A dryade is the spirit of a tree or forest.
My Forest Sensitivity skill allows me to spread my roots throughout the forest,
telling me everything that goes on in it.
I observed your powers, as well.
Can you read my memories, too?
Then why do you look like a child?
It just seemed like something you would like.
I-I am not exactly... into little kids.
So what is this request you have for me?
There is something sucking on me.
There is something creepy sucking away at my whole body.
You are messing with me, are not you?!
Some kind of monster is taking advantage of that
to ravish me day and night while sapping my mana.
If you defeat the monster and save me,
I will tell you where the two treasure chests are, and how to get to the eighth floor.
If I can get more rare treasures, I can help Lola win.
I will need to know more about the monster before I agree to this.
I am a Dryade, so call me Dory!
So that is your real body?
The monster is near the trunk.
There are monsters called Bronze Bees on this level, but that one bee is gold.
I am sure it is some kind of mutation.
It does not seem to have any friends nearby.
That thing will kill me the instant I attack it.
It was rude of me to ask you that out of the blue.
Thank you for hearing me ou
It is sucking up her mana from her real body!
I hate to admit it, but I cannot defeat that bee right now.
I cannot put my life on the line for someone I just met.
Her real body is falling apart.
If it stings her just one more time...
Thank you for hearing me out.
I will show you how to get to the eighth floor.
She must be in so much pain...
I am sorry for troubling you.
You do not have to worry about defeating the mon
Not when you are hurting so much!
Besides, you look so much like her...
Like my dear friend... when she was little.
If I lick it, it will heal faster.
I-If Master saw me in this situation...
Could you wait a little while?
The student relying on his master in his moment of need!
I have been waiting for this!
It seems like it is pretty powerful.
Honestly, I would like you to just ignore this one.
It would be extremely difficult for you to win this fight right now.
I really do not want you to die.
But I do not have any choice.
You fall for the loli tree spirit?
If I do not save her, she is going to die.
Plus, she looks just like a very close friend of mine.
If I just let her die...
I feel like I would never be able to smile at her again.
I will tell you how you can win.
But you would better not die.
I will go all the way to Hell to punch you if you do.
Well, I will not be going to Heaven.
I am a bad girl, after all!
We found the Golden Bee's nest using Dory's Forest Sensitivity skill.
First, let us go forward with step one of our plan.
I will Get Creative, create the skill Target,
and use it on the Golden Bee.
Allows hostile enemies to target the skill holder more easily.
This is where it gets dangerous.
Make sure you come back safe.
And the rest is up to me.
Okay, this is just like that time with the dragon...
Now to make it to the Golden Bee's nest...
It was just at the nest...
The Hidden Dungeon Only I Can Enter!
They keep coming straight for me.
The Target skill I Bestowed earlier!
Allows hostile enemies to target the skill holder more easily.
Allows hostile enemies to target the skill holder more easily.
Allows hostile enemies to target the skill holder more easily, especially by Silver Wolves, who will consider it their natural enemy.
So how do the monsters in the forest on the seventh floor get along?
From what I saw, the Silver Wolves really seemed to look out for each other.
That might work to your advantage.
I call it the... Yesterday's Enemy Is Today's Pawn strategy!
Creates a drop of fresh water.
I will use Editor on Water Drop.
Creates a drop of fresh or sea water.
I could not help at all.
You managed to give me more LP.
A-Anyway, the reason we were able to take down such a powerful enemy
Right in there is where you will find what I wanted to give you as thanks.
But it is a pretty tight squeeze...
Then I will go get them for you.
These were the two items inside the treasure chests.
Get Creative and Create the skill Discerning Eye for Items.
This would be great for Emma, since she has the wind attribute!
This was definitely worth all the trouble!
Wow, this place was really hard to find.
I never would have found it on my own.
We will see each other again soon.
Next time, I will bring something yummy from my world.
Let us keep doing our best together!
I then gave the rare item to Lola...
And the day of her battle against Sarah finally arrived.
I will now announce the receptionist ranking for the Adventurer Guild Odin.
We have been waiting for this!
We have already converted each receptionist's scores into chips,
which have been given to their respective adventurers.
Each adventurer will reveal one chip at a time,
and the last one remaining will be the victor.
The chips were placed one by one,
and the other adventurers around me tapped out one after another.
It all comes down to Sarah and Lola.
I knew it would be these two!
Has Lola run out of points?
Lola is the queen of the receptionists!
That is the only way she could have won!
You cannot say I cheated if you do not have any proof.
Anyway, I won, so do not ever steal anyone else's adventurers again.
I cannot believe this broke my streak...
Coming in second is great, too!
Oh, you are the only one who understands me, Noir!
how to get to Sarah's house?
Who are you callin' a demon?!
Well, anyway, everything's peaceful again at Odin.
The thing is, I want you to... step on me.
There are some people who are into that kind of thing...
And my LP did shoot up with Ms. Elna sitting on me, too...
Are not you embarrassed, making your little sister do this?
